                Pro salute <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan>(domini) <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostri</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>laribus basis <lb n="3"/>marmoreas IIII <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>tur</abbr><ex>ibulum</ex></expan> tumulum <lb n="5"/>haeneam lucerna <lb n="6"/>biluci <expan><abbr>mon</abbr><ex>eta</ex></expan> aerea <lb n="7"/>tabulas encausto <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>picta</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> IIII clypeum <lb n="9"/>et velum <lb n="10"/>Optatus <expan><abbr>ser</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan>(vus) <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ua</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ecunia</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Verschollen. Weder als echt noch als falsa im CIL aufgenommen. (B): Veny: Z. 10: Optatus Sev(erus).</p>
